The paper discusses the Semantic Web and Linked Data, which are related to databases and information retrieval (cs.DB and cs.IR). The tool Path Outlines is designed to support LD producers in browsing their datasets, which involves aspects of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also presents a visualisation technique for path-based summaries, which falls under the category of information visualisation (cs.SI).
